name: BRYLIE
description:
BRYLIE

BRYLIE is a visualization of someone who is strong and ambitious in her/his future. She/He doesn't care about her/his past full of failures. She/He knows where She/he wants to go and She/he is not easily influenced. Don't care about other people's judgments. She/He keep going and keep walking towards her/his goal.

Watercolor on cold press paper 200gsm
3000 X 3000 Pixel

Personal use only.
